{
  "abstract": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "A multilevel accelerator button is a variation of a normal accelerator button that allows for a configurable number of stepped pressure levels. As each one is reached, the user receives light tactile feedback and an action is sent."
    }
  ],
